eiben. Die von Ostberlin forcierte Legendenbildung um Wehners Verhalten in Schweden gibt zudem neue Aufschlüsse über Mechanismen kommunistischer Kaderpolitik und Erpressungsmethoden der Staatssicherheit.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aCommunistszGermanyvBiography. 0aStatesmenzGermanyvBiography. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 1990 - 1999z9783110635867oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978348664570540uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/9783486703061zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486703061zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486703061/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GHIc1990d1999  aZDB-23-GOA